caption:
A couple weeks ago Emily had the pleasure of training alongside a Syracuse lashing icon. For more than 8 years Holly has brought great education to our area. 

I’m personally lucky enough to call her my lash bestie. 

As a student not only do you receive impeccable training - but it’s the support you have following that blows me away. I can reach out to Holly anytime for any question and she’s always there to troubleshoot. 

We @thelashfactory can not recommend her trainings enough. 

What did Emily learn? 

✨ advanced mapping for eye shapes / styles

✨ advanced placement techniques - for better retention and longevity 

✨ taping & planning out your set to make the most of your time. 

✨ business aspects of the lash industry
